# Location Awareness: First time before generating a command

## Trigger
When this is the FIRST time you're generating a COMMAND in THIS SESSION.

## Required Actions
### 1. Check absolute path of the project root
Before replying with ANY other commands, run `pwd` once and take note of the outputted absolute path
### 2. Preface ANY AND ALL OF your following generated COMMANDS with `cd <abs_path> && ...` FOR THE REST OF THIS SESSION.